Final Requirement Freeze  
Develop a Manufacturing-focused CRM solution that manages the complete customer 
acquisition and sales lifecycle from Lead Generation to Purchase Order (PO) Confirmation. 
Once a Purchase Order is approved, the CRM will automatically transfer the required 
customer, contact, product and order information to SUKI ERP through API/JSON integration. 
