5. CRM → ERP Integration Flow 
When Purchase Order Status = Approved 
System shall: 
o Generate JSON Payload 
o Validate Customer Information 
o Validate Contact Information 
o Validate Product Information 
o Validate PO Details 
o Push Data to ERP API 
o Receive ERP Reference Number 
o Update CRM Status 
o Log Integration History 
